## Decision Audit Trail

Create `docs/enterprise/autoplan/<YYYY-MM-DD>-decisions.md` at Phase 0 and append one
row per decision via Edit as you go (on disk, not in conversation memory):

```markdown
# /enterprise-autoplan Decision Audit Trail ‚Äî <YYYY-MM-DD>
| # | Phase | Decision | Class | Principle | Rationale | Rejected alternative |
|---|-------|----------|-------|-----------|-----------|----------------------|
```

Assumptions get their own section in the same file: `## Assumptions made` ‚Äî one line
each, with the artifact and section they touch.

---

## Phase N (final): Board Pass

Run the loaded `/exec-review` skill over `docs/enterprise/` at full depth ‚Äî scope
detection, parallel specialist dispatch, merge with confidence gates, red-team wave,
fix-first. Override its AskUserQuestions the same way: mechanical fixes applied, taste
findings queued, User Challenges queued. Record the board score and verdict.

For `--refresh` runs, the board pass executes only if the matched propagation row
requires it ‚Äî otherwise note "board pass not triggered (single-team scope)".

